products.title: Cup Cake 1
products.description: Method. Heat oven to 180C/160C fan/gas 4 and fill a 12 cupcake tray with cases. Bake for 15 mins until golden brown and a skewer inserted into the middle of each cake comes out clean. To make the buttercream, whisk the butter until super soft then add the icing sugar, vanilla extract and a pinch of salt.
